    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund all payment fees for EpiPens and asthma inhalers",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Fund all payment fees for EpiPens and asthma inhalers to make them free of charge. These medicines are critical for managing life-threatening conditions and are required for immediate emergency treatment. We believe it is unreasonable for such essential medication to come at a cost.",
